      </div>
      <div class="info-card">
        <strong>Immune defense — mucosal integrity</strong>
        <p>Vitamin A maintains the mucosal barriers in the respiratory tract, GI tract, and urinary system. It also supports T-cell production and antibody responses, making it critical for adaptive immunity.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="info-card">
